data.description:
Exquisite local artist inspired quality custom built one level home in sought after Orcutt Estates offers every attention to detail!  Enjoy amazing unobstructed views from every window on the back side of this gorgeous 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath, approx. 2,607 sq ft charming English Cottage with a Tuscan flare.  Home features an open & split floorplan, high ceilings, classic archways, gorgeous chisel edge tile floors, recessed lighting, lighted display art niches and many special custom features throughout.  The fantastic gourmet kitchen has top of the line stainless steel appliances, lighted walk-in pantry, large island & breakfast bar with pendant lighting open to the wonderful sunny nook & living area with fireplace & plenty of windows for natural lighting.  Separate generous size formal dining room is the perfect setting for large dinner gatherings.  The Primary suite retreat has amazing views, dual sinks, oversize walk-in shower, huge walk-in closet & private door to back.  Guest Bedroom/office/previous art studio has exterior French door access that opens to a sweet private patio, perfect powder room with pedestal sink.  2 additional guest bedrooms on opposite end share a full bathroom with dual sinks. Large Indoor laundry room with plenty of storage, 3-car finished garage, tankless water heater & much more!  Situated on a sprawling beautifully landscaped .77-acre lot with raised garden beds for your gardening pleasure.  This stunning home has everything you need & more! Short distance to Old Town Orcutt, where you can enjoy fantastic eateries, bakeries/coffee, wine tasting, breweries, and small hometown shops.  Easy access to Hwy 1 & Vandenberg SFB.
*** BUYER BONUS:  Beautiful interior furnishings including original wall paintings and outdoor patio furniture may be included with acceptable offer.
